snippet.title: Trailer - An Action Roguelite for when you have 20 minutes to spare
snippet.description:
Wishlist now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2354200/An_Action_Roguelite_for_when_you_have_20_minutes_to_spare/

A quick and fun roguelite about divin', jumpin' n' shootin'. Fight through five stages of weird beasties and OP upgrades.

Soundtrack by tenby and Wangleline
https://wangleline.bandcamp.com/album/splashnode
Check it out!
